foundry-linux-ios-development (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Metapackage for the Linux-side iOS development
    toolchain — libimobiledevice-utils, ideviceinstaller, usbmuxd,
    ifuse. The actual iOS build runs on macOS via Codemagic; this
    package covers the device-communication side. The companion
    install script also pipx-installs codemagic-cli-tools (pip-only,
    inexpressible as a Depends:).

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Wed, 20 May 2026 04:00:00 +0000


